high_descs: Turn around to the green island.
Pick up the knife from the front, in front of the pan.
Carry the knife and turn around to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the knife.
Take the knife and turn around to the island.
Place the knife and on the left side of the island, just behind where it originally was.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight slightly then turn right and face to the green counter
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the edge of the counter
Turn around and walk straight up to the sink and face it
Place the knife in the sink and turn on the water to rinse then remove the knife
Turn around and walk straight up to the kitchen counter and face it
Place the knife on the counter
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a yellow handled knife

high_descs: Wash the knife in the sink
Place the knife down on the table
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife and put it back
